{"tid":1631541,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人權法都未過 大家睇風向 隨時逆轉","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:45:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T20:25:04.000Z","uid":104819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ae43658fb23c0aa6210768edcff52bbf405bf53a","tid":1631541,"uid":104819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:45:25.000Z","msg":"已經有議員不同意臨時政府 人權法推上去變左難 <br />\n<br />\n民意有所改變 希望可以停一停一陣 唔好俾人覺得我地只係得破壞 市民都想休息下 <br />\n<br />\n文宣繼續可以發展下 呢排已經好少好少 基乎得番獅了 互屌 玩分化<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後 我<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">不分化 不割席</span></span>"},{"pid":"d042406d8ec8fd998109b5febd3ff5ef06fb0521","tid":1631541,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:46:19.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"0fc577934a6f649c43a679e1ab5609435925bb8b","tid":1631541,"uid":104819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:46:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18561a98129ff3a2802e12d373ed2984b6be9c3a","tid":1631541,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:47:12.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n記唔記得當初應承過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈都唔割</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣洗地</span></strong></span>開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a028848cc98cc94bb12f7f2cbfc161ae48d0bc2e","tid":1631541,"uid":104819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:49:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d3cbd31548ff569ab3fd6f109e5103848677a9e","tid":1631541,"uid":104819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:54:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8778936f3470fa6c0c0a1e9706a262d4b2db81f0","tid":1631541,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:54:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54021b4908530a3832f91c796edff03c9c842a65","tid":1631541,"uid":104819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:03:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"053b331f503695043a3515c1588523a12a4f9be0","tid":1631541,"uid":104819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:07:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27a1cc1a829ef5e647f28ec9db1f78d5231f0166","tid":1631541,"uid":104819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:09:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b6572ba381efb207efea0268755f3161eaaa1c3","tid":1631541,"uid":104819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-